---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "January 27, 2026";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Poster Magic">
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 py-20 px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <header class="mb-12 text-center">
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-500 mb-4"
                >
                    Poster Magic Privacy Policy
                </h1>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
            </header>

            <article
                class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-300"
            >
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        1. Introduction
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Sunbreak LLC ("we," "our," or "us") operates the Poster
                        Magic mobile application. We respect your privacy and
                        are committed to protecting the personal information you
                        share with us.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        This Privacy Policy explains what information we
                        collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that
                        data.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        2. Information We Collect
                    </h2>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-6 mb-2">
                        A. Account Information
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        When you create an account, we use Google Firebase
                        Authentication to verify your identity. Depending on the
                        method you choose (Sign in with Apple, Google, Email, or
                        SMS), we may process:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>Email address</li>
                        <li>Phone number</li>
                        <li>User ID (assigned by Firebase)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p
                        class="mt-4 p-4 bg-slate-900 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 rounded-r text-slate-300 italic"
                    >
                        <strong>Note:</strong> We do not store your email or phone
                        number in our own separate database; this information resides
                        within the secure Firebase Authentication infrastructure.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-2">
                        B. User Content (Photos and Images)
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        To provide the core functionality of Poster Magic, you
                        upload photos to our service.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Transient Processing:</strong> Your photos are
                            uploaded securely to our cloud servers solely for the
                            purpose of processing them with our AI engine.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>No Permanent Storage:</strong> Once the AI analysis
                            is complete and the response is returned to your device,
                            the original photo is permanently deleted from our servers.
                            We do not retain your photos.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-2">
                        C. Technical Data and Logs
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        We collect certain technical data to ensure the app is
                        stable and to debug errors. This includes:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Device Information:</strong> Device model, OS
                            version, and unique device identifiers.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Usage Logs:</strong> Anonymized logs of app crashes
                            or errors.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>IP Address:</strong> Collected automatically by
                            our infrastructure providers for security and fraud prevention.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        3. How We Use Your Information
                    </h2>
                    <p>We use your data for the following specific purposes:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong>To Provide the Service:</strong> Authenticating
                            your login and processing your photos to generate poster
                            content.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>AI Processing:</strong> We use Google Cloud (Gemini)
                            to analyze your photos. We have configured our systems
                            to opt-out of data logging for model training. Your data
                            is not used to train Google’s AI models.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>App Stability:</strong> We use Firebase Crashlytics
                            and Firebase Analytics to identify crashes and improve
                            app performance.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        4. Third-Party Service Providers
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        We do not sell your data. We share data only with the
                        trusted third-party infrastructure providers necessary
                        to run the app:
                    </p>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                        <table
                            class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[600px]"
                        >
                            <thead>
                                <tr class="border-b border-slate-700">
                                    <th
                                        class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-white"
                                        >Provider</th
                                    >
                                    <th
                                        class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-white"
                                        >Purpose</th
                                    >
                                    <th
                                        class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-white"
                                        >Privacy Policy</th
                                    >
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr class="border-b border-slate-800">
                                    <td class="py-3 px-4">Google Firebase</td>
                                    <td class="py-3 px-4"
                                        >Authentication, Database, & Analytics</td
                                    >
                                    <td class="py-3 px-4"
                                        ><a
                                            href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
                                            class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors"
                                            target="_blank"
                                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                            >Google Privacy Policy</a
                                        ></td
                                    >
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="border-b border-slate-800">
                                    <td class="py-3 px-4"
                                        >Google Cloud (Gemini)</td
                                    >
                                    <td class="py-3 px-4"
                                        >AI Image Processing</td
                                    >
                                    <td class="py-3 px-4"
                                        ><a
                                            href="https://cloud.google.com/terms/cloud-privacy-notice"
                                            class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors"
                                            target="_blank"
                                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                            >Google Cloud Privacy</a
                                        ></td
                                    >
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        5. Data Retention and Deletion
                    </h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Photos:</strong> Deleted immediately after processing.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Generated Content:</strong> The .ics (calendar)
                            files and poster images generated by the app are stored
                            locally on your device. We do not store copies of these
                            on our servers.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Account Deletion:</strong> You have the right
                            to delete your account at any time directly within the
                            app settings. When you request deletion:
                            <ul
                                class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-400"
                            >
                                <li>
                                    Your authentication credentials are removed
                                    from Firebase.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Any associated user ID data is permanently
                                    wiped.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        6. Children’s Privacy
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Poster Magic is intended for a general audience. We do
                        not knowingly collect personal information from children
                        under the age of 13. If we become aware that we have
                        inadvertently collected data from a child under 13, we
                        will take steps to delete it immediately.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                        7. Contact Us
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or
                        your data, please contact us at:
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <a
                            href="mailto:xondeck@outlook.com"
                            class="text-xl text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors"
                            >xondeck@outlook.com</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </section>
            </article>

            <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 text-center">
                <a
                    href="/"
                    class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors"
                    >← Back to Home</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
